 <h2>Further Hunting in Paludal Caverns</h2><br><br><br>Paludal is an insanely good exp zone for lower levels. Especially for Mages, as we can solo well here. As a Mage you should never take a bandits group, its just not worth it exp wise.<br><br>Soloing is the way, or duo or similar with another high dps class. There are a few great spots in this zone, coming out from ShadowHaven you will pass a lone shroom spawn, this is a fantastic camp, alternatively invis and head down and right, through the bandits, and you will see a ramp covered in fiends. These are great to solo, just DS and Burnout pet and send it in, then either heal or nuke. If your pet gets hit with their DoT the low level pet heal will remove it as well as restoring hp.<br><br><br>Happy hunting.<br><br><br><br></center><b><u>Zone Information:</u></b><br><br><a href='http://www.eqmages.com' onClick='moblist(148); return false;'>Paludal Caverns mob list</a><br>
<a href='http://www.eqmages.com' onClick='questlist(148); return false;'>Paludal Caverns quest list</a><br><a href='http://www.eqatlas.com/luclin/paludalcaverns.html'>Paludal Caverns Map</a><br><br><b><u>Comments/Feedback:</u></b><br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>BULLSHIT the best one can do in Paludal Caverns is to get in a Bandit group!!!!!<br><br><i><b>triffle</b> says:</i><br>anonymous obviously you dont know what you are talking about with an comment like that. maybe someday you will learn how to play the game and find out that soloing/duoing is easily better xp than sharing xp with 5 other people (the group xp bonus doesnt come close to making up the difference) and trying to get in a bandit camp where you get to, as usual, split either B1 or B2 with another group and wait for pops. Learn the game before you comment next time
<br><br><i><b>Toblik</b> says:</i><br>i agree that soloing or duoing is better but as a level 23 the feinds sucked so badly. i cleared entire zone of feind (about 30) and i didn't even get 2 blue bubbles of exp. horrible in my opinion.  the best exp i found was soloing B2, although very tough i didn't use any mana for nukes only heals.  try it out, but only pull one or 2 at a time and come from the feind side (right side).<br><br><form action='rate.php' method='post' name='rate'>
